    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, always garaged, and drives like a cloud. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
