    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L high-revving straight-six. This specimen boasts a flawless mechanical pedigree, with the VANOS system fully serviced and the rear subframe proactively reinforced for maximum torsional rigidity. The naturally aspirated powerplant breathes through individual throttle bodies, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response and a linear power band up to its 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic steering feedback and lateral stability this chassis is renowned for. Meticulously maintained with no deferred maintenance, this is a turnkey investment for the serious purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
