      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and ceramic-coated since day one. The exterior is flawless, featuring a deep, glass-like finish with absolutely no rock chips, dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the black Dakota leather with contrast blue stitching remains taut and supple, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma; the bolsters show zero wear. With only 12,000 miles, the engine bay is spotless, and every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection. No track time, no modifications, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
